Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:18.74,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Even though it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.95,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…even though I feel sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:29.28,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…in the court I feel just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:37.48,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,When I hear the ball flying, my heart races.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:41.56,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Receive. Toss. Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:46.55,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,One-two, one-two! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:49.35,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,But sometimes I cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:52.41,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,I'm a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:01:00.68,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Through the tears and sweat, putting up a youthful fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:08.82,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…under the blue sky, I just want to scream:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:16.98,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:26.12,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{あしたに賭ける}Episode 002\NThe Gamble for Tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:02:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{一二。一二。一二。一二。}One-two! One-two!\NOne-two! One-two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{あーもうダメ。}I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{なに言ってんの、これぐらいで。}This is nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、立って。}Come on, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{苦しいも。}It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはもうダメ。}I've had enough too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{ダメダメ、こんなことじゃ。さ、立って。}This won't get you anywhere. Come on, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、XXX砂XXXましょうよ。}Hey, how about we run somewhere else without sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXだからいいのよ。足腰お鍛えには砂地はが一番もの。}While it'd feel easier, running on sand is the best for training your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。あの灯台までもうXXXよ。}Now, one more lapse to the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{はーあんな遠くまで？}That far…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかりして。相手はバレー部のレギュラーよ。}Get it together. Our opponents are volleyball club's regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{このぐらいで値を上げてたら、勝ってこないでしょ？}If we admit defeat here, we'll never win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。親分の言う通りだわ。}It's just as the chief says.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{やるといったら、死ぬまでやるのよ。}Let's keep at it until we pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのいち。そのいち。}Exactly, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ。出発行こう。}Well then, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{あー待って。}Ah… wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{まってよー}Wait for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。皆頑張って。}Let's do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX,行くわよ。}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。ほら、XXXしっかりやって。}Pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーすみません。ーXXXこのぐらいにしたら？}- I'm sorry.\N- Isn't this enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{ダメダメ。}It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX様そんなこと言っちゃ困るじゃないの。}It's bad if you start thinking that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、相手は白いと同然の不良グループよ。}But our opponents are just a bunch of newcomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX立って勝ってないよ。}There's no way they could win with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{油断は禁物。}Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらさんはなにを考えてるか警戒しないと。}We've no idea what Ayuhara-san's plans might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは大丈夫よ。}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{彼女が一人頑張ったって。}She might be doing her best, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほかる五人はXXX}…you can't say that about the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{一二。一二。一二。一二。}One-two! One-two!\NOne-two! One-two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、頑張って。}Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう辞めちゃう、あたしは。}Maybe I should quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{これ以上やったら、本当に死んじゃうわ。}If I keep at this, I'll pass out for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{また。あんたたち、そんなXX気がどうすんなよ。}Again? What's with that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、立って。最後まで頑張るのよ。}Come on. Last few steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{もうたくさん。}I've had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX、バレーなんかあたしたちに無理だったのよ。}Looks like volleyball is impossible for us after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。相手はほんとうのバレー部たち。やるXXXきゃむりよ。お腹がすく-}Yeah. Our opponents are genuine volleyball club members. I'm hungry all t—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと、あんたたち、それ本気？}Hey, are you serious about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうだよ。こんあことしてらXXXゴゴXXX楽しいXXX}Yep. Go go dancing is much more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{二人とも、甘ったれないで。}Don't get so soft, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{まって、なかざわさん。}Hold on, Nakazawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あんまり…}But those two…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいから。あたしに任してちょうだい。}It's all right. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXけもっとXXXいいわ。／打ちだけもっと打てばいいわ。}Hit me all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{とにかく、あたしXXXもらうわ。}Anyway, I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{あー待って}Ah… wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分、どうする？}Chief, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちこそ、どうする？}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはたとえ一人なったってやるのよ。}Even if I'm all alone, I'll still do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーあたしも。ーもちろん、あたしも。}- Me too.\N- Of course me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう。}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、やりましょう。}Let's continue then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{あのふたりともきっとそのうち分かってくれるわ。}They will come to their senses soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーうん。やるわ。ーXXXなったら、四人だっていいわよ。}- All right. Let's continue.\N- We'll go on with just the 4 of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも四人でバレーはできない。}But we can't play with just 4 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{あのふたりをなんとかしなきゃ大変なことになるわ。}It'll be bad if I don't get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。しかし、諦めるのはまだ早いじゃないか。}Hmm. It's still too early to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろんあたしだって完全に諦めたわけじゃないけど…}I have no intention of giving up, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{トレーニング大事に決めで脱落XXXのふたりも出ちゃう。}Two of them have already dropped out of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{とても自身ないわ。}I don't believe in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、バレー部に試合中止をもうしれるのか？}With things like this, shouldn't you suspend the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{残念だけど、そう言うことに…}It's a shame, but… I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、それじゃ…彼女達をXXXさせるだけだよ、あゆはらくん。}If you don't, you'll be only giving the other girls false hopes, Ayuhara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{元々、あたしの計画は無理だったのね。}Looks like my plan was absurd to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{弱きだな。きみらしくないぞ。}That's weak. It doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、四人でどうにも試合にはならないもの。}But it's impossible to hold a match with just 4 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい。ーXXX。ーはい。それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って。もう一つ。}Do your best. One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って。さ！}Keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{なるほど。そう言えば、バレー部の練習はいつもと違います。}I see. By the way, volleyball club's practice seems to be more intense lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{いじでも、かしわぎやなかざまグループに負けたくないからでしょう。}That's because they don't want to lose to the Kashiwagi's group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、あゆはらこずえもなんであんな不良グループのかたおもつんでしょうな。}But why is Ayuhara Kozue staying with these delinquents, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かりませんね。}I don't get it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{めいほう学園から来たXXXしてはXXXますよ。}She transferred from Meihou Academy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ、そそそ。結局取り柄はバレーだけって子じゃないですか、あゆはらこずえは。}That's right. Ultimately, the volleyball isn't her only redeeming feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？めいほう学園ですって？}Eh? Meihou Academy, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうなのよ。東京でも仲裁XXXの秀才が集まってる。あのめいほう学園よ。}Yeah. The one in Tokyo that only accepts the best among the best students. That Meihou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、バレー部も有名な名門校よ?}Then, their volleyball club must be famous too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かったわ。それだあたしたちバレー部をバカにしたんだわ。}That's why she made fun of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうなると、XXX油断できないわね。}We can't let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも信じられないわね。}But I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{彼女はめいほうの秀才だなんて…}For her to be a Meihou's prodigy…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくらいい学校でもピンからキリまでいるわ。}Even the best school has its worst students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{わが富士見学園のようにね。}Just like our Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。だからあゆはらさんもしかしたら退学処分にでもなって…}Yeah. With that in mind, perhaps Ayuhara-san got expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、ちょっとちょっとちょっと。聞いた。}Hey, listen, listen, listen.\NGot news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらさんってめいほう学園X退学処分になった人何だって。}Ayuhara-san got expelled from Meihou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。それでここへ来ても不良グループと付き合ってのね。}And now that she came to our school, she started hanging out with the delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと。}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたち今なんて言ったのよ。}What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？え…なー何も…}Eh? N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{べつにあなたたちのこと不良グループって言ってわけじゃ…}It's not like we called you delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなこと聞いてないわよ。}Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらさんは退学処分なったと話どこから聞いたXXX言うのよ。}Where did you hear that Ayuhara-san was expelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの…それはバレー部の人から。}Err… from a member of the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんですって}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、ね！ちょっと皆！}Hey, hey! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたのよ、ナカ？}What is it, Naka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーバレー部…殴り込むよ。ーバレー部へ？}- We're gonna attack the volleyball club.\N- Wait, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。あの連中ったらね、あゆはらさんは東京の学校退学処分なんて声がXXXなんて。}Yeah. They're telling a story that Ayuhara-san was expelled from a school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆に言い触らしちゃってのよ。}They're spreading this rumor to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう勘弁できないわ。あんたたちも来て。}I can't let it slide any longer. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{いこう？}Should we go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもやる。}I'll still do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし最後まで諦めないわ。}I won't give up till the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{人事を尽くして、天命を待つか？}One does what one can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい。親分、大変よ！}Hey! Chief, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{あのね、ナカXXXたちわね、バレー部に殴り込むかけに行っちゃったXXX。どうする。}Listen, Naka and the others went to attack the volleyball club. What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？あたし行ってみる。}Eh? I'll go and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、皆、なんとか言ったらどうなのよ。}Why do you go around saying whatever you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{なによ。退学なった人は退学なったって何が悪いのよ。}What's wrong with calling expulsion for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、何もそんな言い触らしないでもいいでしょう。}Even if she was expelled, that's no reason to spread it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{別に言い触らしたりしないわ。ただ自然に噂を広がっただけよ。}It's not like we're spreading rumors on purpose. It spread naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。おこることないでしょう。}Yeah. There's nothing to be upset about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらさんはあなたたちのグループのボスに相応しい人だってこと分かったんだから。}People now understand that Ayuhara-san is a fitting boss for your group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなことXXXわよ。}Those are some big words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日はどうしても決着付けるから。思って出て。}Today I'll fix this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。飽きれたわ。}I've had enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{暴力に訴えるXXXね、バレーでXXX。}Because you can't beat us in volleyball, you're going to resort to violence, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのとおりよ。}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーなんかあんな面倒くさいゲームだってもうごめんよ。}Volleyball is such a boring game anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはもう辞めたわ。}I'm already out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{おや、ま、そうなの。}Oh my, is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{是非XXX辞めにしたの。}Did you really quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{だったら、あゆはらさんから人事挨拶だってもういいじゃないの。}You don't care about Ayuhara-san, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だ辞めたって決めたわけじゃないわよ。}We haven't decided whether to quit yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、あら。もう内輪もめ？}Oh my. Family trouble already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんな女子XXXとてもバレーは無理ね。}Volleyball is so out of reach for you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{うるさい。}Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーXXX!ー何してんのXXX}- What do you know!\N- What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{待って。}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーあゆはらさん。ー事情はかしわぎさんから聞いたわ。}- Ayuhara-san.\N- I heard about it from Kashiwagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、暴力に訴えるなんて卑怯よ。}But resorting to the violence is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{卑怯でもなんだって、いいわよ。}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{ダメ。事情はXXX手を出したら負けよ。}Wrong. The moment you lose your cool, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなことしてごらんなさい。}But fine, be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXとあなたたちは退学よ。}You'll get expelled in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{それじゃ、バレー部の人達の思うツボじゃないの。}With that, you'll play right into volleyball club's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、あんまりXXXだから。}But they're so impudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かるわ。}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、その気持ちを今度の試合ぶっつけるのよ。}But vent your feelings in the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かってくれる？}Can you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分の言う通りよ。}It's as the chief says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、皆。この部は親分の顔ほ立てって,私達は引き上げることにしない？}Everyone. Let's save our chief's face and withdraw for now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいわ。}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう。}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXしてちょうだい。}Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ。この決着は必ず付けて見せるわ。}We'll surely settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたち、覚えていらっしゃい。}You better remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{んだ。}Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{んだ。}Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{ベーダ。}Booo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXでした。}Looks like I calmed them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{ふん。さすがあゆはらさんですね。}As expected from Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{いい子XXXおもって、XXXこと。}She must regard herself as a good chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{池崎さんと大木さんはどこに行ったの？}Where did Ikezaki-san and Ooki-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりダメ。}It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{喧嘩なら、見方するけど、バレーはごめんですって。}They allied for the quarrel, but their decision didn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ…}Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもあたしは諦めないわ。}But I'm not giving up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あの様子じゃ…}What a mess…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。諦めない。}I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{最後の最後まで、あたしは粘っている。}I'll persist till the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーおはよう。ーおはよう。}- Good morning.\N- Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーおはよう。ーおはよう。}- Morning.\N- Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{なにかしら？}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。中間テストの成績発表よ。}Ah. Midterm tests results are in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。ベストXXXけど。}It only shows the best results though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたち縁のない話ね。}It doesn't concern us, does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと、大変よ。大ニュース。}Hey, listen! Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらさんはテストに一番成ったんのよ。}Ayuhara-san has the highest score.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？そんなバカな。}Huh? That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXってダメよ。／担ぐXXXってダメよ。}Don't deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当よ。それでXXXじゃない。}It's the truth. Come see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。本当。}Ah. She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらさんは一番だわ。}Ayuhara-san is the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体どんな勉強したの?}What sort of method did you study with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、別に。}Nothing particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらくん。}Ayuhara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕は…今までずっと一番だったんだぜ。}Until now, I've been the first all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{それを…エスケープのイメージの君に向かれるなんて…}Having you, a delinquent, surpass me…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{信じられないな。}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなバカなことってないわよ。}There's no way you'd pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{絶対可笑しいわよ。}It's very fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しいってどう言うこと？}Fishy how?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{何かやったんじゃないかってことさ。}She means you must have done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{なにか？}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。例えば、カンニングとか。}Yeah. For example, you cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんですって？}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{失礼なこと言わないで。}Don't be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。カンニングがなんて…あたしたちの親分に変なXXX承知しないから。}Yeah. If you make such statements about our chief, we won't stand by idle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと。なんとか言ったらどうなの？}Hey, how about you say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは、カンニングしたって証拠でもあるの？}Do you have any proof that I cheated?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{あるさ。}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{だってそうだろう？}Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{めいほう学園を退学処分になった君は、いくら程度が違うからって、}After expulsion from the Meihou Academy, no matter how different our level is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{この学校へ来て、急に一番とれるわけないじゃないか。}…there's no way you'd suddenly get the best score.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。何時あたしが退学処分になんかなって？}My. When did I get expelled from anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはそうじゃないかった、あたしの…}So that's not how it was? Then, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい、おい。君達。}Whoa, whoa. You guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{失礼なこと言っちゃいかんよ。}You can't say rude things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生…}Professor…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらくんはめいほう学園でずっと首席XXX人だよ。}Ayuhara-kun always stood at the top in the Meihou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーま、首席-ーカンニングなんて失礼もういいとこだわ。}- At the top…\N- Now you see how much of an insult your claim was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{すげー。}Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXさん。お気の毒様。}Too bad, Miura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ、あたしはショックだわ。あの人はめいほう学園の首席だなんて。}Ah, I'm in shock. For her to be at the top of the Meihou Academy…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{丸であたしたちはバカみたいじゃないの。}I feel like we've made fools of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。こうなったら、せめてバレーでXXXわ。}All right, Now that it came to this, let's show our strength through volleyball to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。どんなことXXX、負けられないわ。}Yeah. We mustn't lose to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりあたしたちの騙されてたなのよ。}She tricked us after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{なによ貫禄十分の親分よ。}She's plenty dignified without being our chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{全然あたしたちのXXX違うじゃないの。}She's totally different from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも不思議だわ。そんなXXX全然見えないもう。}But life sure is strange. I didn't saw it coming at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたの？こんな所に集まって…}What are you doing gathered like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、それは…いや、全然いいじゃない…}Ah, this… we're, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{変XXXあなたたち。}You're acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、酷いわ、あゆはらさんも。}But sure you're cruel, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{なにが？}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、めいほう学園の大秀才だってこと…あたしたちに隠したりしてさ。}I mean you hiding your status at Meihou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、別に隠したりなんかしてないわ。}Oh, it's not like I've been hiding it with malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{ただ、そんなこと自慢にもならないから黙ってだけよ。}It's just that if I haven't stayed silent, it'd come across as boasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あなたはあたしたちと別世界の人よ。}But you're in a different world from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX大秀才XXXあたしたちXXXには付き合いXXXわ。}A prodigy like you has no business in hanging out with losers like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたち本気そんなこと言ってるの？}Are you saying this seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{退学になったころ仲間で首席じゃだめなの？}That we can't be friends just because I happen to have good grades?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはあたし。あゆはらこずえよ。}I am me. Ayuhara Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{一緒にバレー部やっつけるおとしじゃないの？ね、そうでしょう？}Weren't we going to take on the volleyball club together? Wasn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん…}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーでも…ー本当にそう思う？}- But…\N- Do you really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。それでなきゃ最初からあなたたちとお友達してないかならないわ。}Yeah. If I didn't, I wouldn't be able to befriend you to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{悔しい思いXXXして殴り込みを止めたりなんかしないわよ。}I wouldn't have the painful {training}memories nor care about the {volleyball club}assault either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ、感激。}Ah, I'm touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりあたしたちの親分だわね。}She's truly our chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、今までXXX付き合ってXXXね。}Then, we can hang around like we used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろんよ。}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{池崎さん。大木さん。}Ikezaki-san. Ooki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちともう一度考え直して、お友達になってくれない？}Why don't we make up and stay friends again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちも？わ…}Us too? Wah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう？}How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{大木さん。}Ooki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちだってバレー部をぎゃふんといらせたいでしょう？}Don't you too want to beat the volleyball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{だから殴り込みの時にとんできたでしょう？}That's why you too came during the assault, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXトレーニングは苦しいわ。}Training sure is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、この苦しいに乗り越えなきゃ。}But we need to overcome its hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{池崎さん。大木さん。}Ikezaki-san. Ooki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーいいわ、あたし。ーあたしもやるわ。}- Okay.\N- I'll do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう。}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちのこと許してくれる?}Will you forgive us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{許すなんて、そんな…}There's nothing to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたち皆同じよ。}We're all on the same page.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{一人かけてもダメよ。}The strength lies in teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{わ。嬉しい。}Wah. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたみたいに秀才の仲間XXXもうバカにするないわ。}We won't make fun of good students like you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。後はバレーだけよ。}Yeah. Now all that's left is to train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。そうと決まったら、皆、頑張ろう。}Ok. Now that it's decided, let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{絶対途中音を上げないのよ。いいわ、ね？}No quitting midway, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、今日から一ヶ月みっちりトレーニングよ。}Then, from today, it's one month of strict training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいわね？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーOK！ーOK！}- Okay!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{これでいいわ。}This should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{後試合を勝つだけだ。}All that's left is to win the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうすれば、この人達だって自身が付くし、何もかもうまくいくわ。}If we win, it will give these girls the confidence they need and everything will go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{一二！一二！一二！一二！}One-two! One-two!\NOne-two! One-two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ！じゃ、いよいよ今日からボールをつかっての練習よ。}All right. From today we'll focus on handling the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{敵に勝つ方法がただ一つ。}There's only one rule to winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{練習。練習。練習よ。}It's practice. Practice. Practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー分かったわね？ーうん。}- Got it?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、なかざわさん、いくわよ。}Okay then. Nakazawa-san, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーOK。ーナカ、頑張って。}- Okay.\N- Naka, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{ダメ。}No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{六人制のバレーではどんな場合でも、パチンなんと落とさせたら、犯則よ。}In 6-player volleyball, if you let yourself lose the ball, it's a foul play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{パスは必ず指先で弾く。}Pass must be done with the fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{OK。}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、往復、行くわよ。}Then, let's do it in turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{行くわよ。}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーあー痛い。ーごめん。}- It hurts.\N- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいわ。}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{これだけファイトXXXば一ヶ月でも間に合えるかもしれない。}If they stay this inspired for a month, we might make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ダメダメ、そんなことじゃ。}This won't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、いくわよ。}All right, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、頑張って。}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日はサーブとサーブレシーブの練習よ。}Today we'll focus on serving and receiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{六人制ではサーブは一回しか打てないから、確実に相手のコートに入れること。}In 6-player system, you only get one serve, so aim to hit the ball into the opponents court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーいい？ーうん。}- Got it?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかり、しっかり。}Pull it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、XXX／頑張って。／立って。}Come on, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}They're really giving their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{この女子だと何か行けるかもしれないわ。}These girls are full of potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{痛い。}It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、指が右に倒れた。XXX}Ah, my finger twisted to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？何言ってるの。}Huh? What are you saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{ただの突き指よ。}It's just a jammed finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{うまくなるには突き指の十回ぐらいは普通よ。}It'll normal to have all 10 fingers jammed at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？十回も？}Eh? All 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}At this rate, my beautiful fingers will get all lumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{冗談言ってる場合はないのよ。}This isn't the time to joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部と試合まであと三週間。}We've got three weeks before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{突き指した人は治るまでジャンプの練習よ。いいわね？}Those with jammed fingers, switch to jumping until healing. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Ehh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{中々やるわね。}She seems to be at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{この低能なら大したことないわ。}The others are pathetic though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。一月の練習で我々に勝ってるわけがないわ。}There's no way they'd win with just 1 month of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。バレー部の連中よ。}Ah. It's the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{ふん。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{検察に来たんだ、きっと。}They came to spy on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{だれが身に来いXXX気にしない、気にしない。}Don't pay attention to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、始めて。}All right, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー試合なんかやるだけもXXX。ーそうね。}- They'll be the same during the match.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{ふん。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{何とでも言いなさいよ。}Say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。人を舐めると承知しないから。}Yeah. You'll pay if you underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{黙って。練習する。}Shut up and practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんなこと言うな、自分たちが不安だから。}They say such things because they're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、始めて、始めて。}Okay. Begin, begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーほんごう先生。ーは？}- Professor Hongou.\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの子たちのこと。どう考えXXXすの？}What do you think about those girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX,おそらく、あなたと同じこと考えています。}I'm probably thinking the same thing as you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}My…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらくんがバレーのコーチを始めてからってもな…}Ever since Ayuhara-kun started coaching the volleyball…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{…教室であの彼女達の怠惰や成績は見違えるようによくなった。}…their diligence in the classroom and their grades have improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{と言うことは、きっと…バレーな彼女達を精神的に立ち直れすXXXかもしれない。}Perhaps with her help, the girls will return to the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうでしょう？}Am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{その通りですわ。}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしXX担任として、あゆはらさん脱帽したい気持ちです。}As her homeroom teacher, I'm taking my hat to Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{いや。まったく同感ですね。}I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし先生、もう少し黙ってみてやりましょうね。}Let's stay silent for a little longer and watch over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{彼女は今、XXX,真剣にバレーに打ち込んじるんですから。}Right now, she's earnestly devoted to the volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX,頑張ってよ。}Keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう行くよ！}One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って、頑張って。}Do your best, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{後三日。}Three days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{技術XXXできるはこのファイトXXXだけわ。}Now that they mastered basic techniques, the match is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{絶対に…絶対に勝って見せるわ。}We will win without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんですって、つとむちゃん？こずえちゃんはバレーボールを？}What do you mean, Tsutomu-chan? Kozue-chan plays volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部相手にやるんだって、XXXよ。}She's taken the volleyball club on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{とれで、このごろ毎日帰りにな遅かったのね。}So that's why she's been coming late recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{叔母さんは知らなかったか？}Auntie, you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{知るもんですか。}How was I supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{毎日図書館で勉強してるとばかり思ってたわ。}I was sure she was studying in the library every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{あーしまったな…}Ah– damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、僕から聞いたこと…内緒にしといてよ。}Then, please keep it a secret that I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうは行けませんよ。}I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえちゃんはバレー何かやっては行けない体なのよ。}Kozue-chan's body won't withstand volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなに悪いの？}It's that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{当たり前じゃないの。}Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{でなきゃ、態々こんな所へ???来るもんですか。}Otherwise, why'd she come all the way here in the middle of the school term.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あんなに元気なのに。}But she looks so full of energy—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{顔だけ見たって分かるもんですか。}You can see it just by looking at her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたはあなたもうじゃないの。なぜもっと早く知らせてくれないの？}You're a responsible boy. Why didn't you tell me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{おー}Err…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{すみません。}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{すみませんじゃすまないぞ。}"Sorry" doesn't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえ自分の体のことは自分が一番知っているだろう。}Kozue is the one that knows her own body the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{だから大丈夫だと思って…}That's why I think it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{いかん。}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{もし悪化したら、大変だ。}We can't let it get any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{直ぐこれから病院へ行こう。}Let's go to the hospital at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、バレー部と試合まで後一日しかないのよ。}But there's only one day before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{今、あたしはXXX引いたら、かしわぎさんたち、グループはどうなるの？}If I withdrew today, what would happen to Kashiwagi-san and our group?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{グループ？}Group?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{やもうえんだろう。}It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうせいこんな試合なんて大したことあるない。}That match cannot be this important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなことないわ。}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{明日の試合にはもっと大事なことかかってるんですもの。}The tomorrow's match means very precious thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{大事なことってなんだ？}What is so precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは…その…}That's… err…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、こうぜちゃん。}Hey, Kozue-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{とにかく、あなたは大事な預かりものなんです。}At any rate, we need to take care of yourself, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパやママたいして、なんと詫びすればいいの？}Otherwise how would we apologize to your mom and dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{お詫びなんて、そんな…ぐずぐず言ってないで。}Apologize? Don't you grumble now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー早く、医者の所へ行こう。ーいやです。}- Let's hurry and go see the doctor.\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえ！}Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえ…}Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、こずえちゃん…}Hey, Kozue-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かったでしょう?}You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{とにかく、お医者様の所いって、レントゲンを撮って貰いましょう、ね？}For time being, at least let's take a radiograph, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしよう？}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.38,0:22:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{もしレントゲンにXXXあったら…}What if something shows up on the radiograph…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえ。}Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{あーはい！}Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士病院}《Fuji Hospital》
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生遅すぎるわ。}The doctor is taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、あたし…むー胸がドキドキして…}My heart is pumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{お前がドキドキすることはXXXない。}Worrying now won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{もうすぐ結果を分かる。}We'll know the results soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{落ち着くんだ。}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{その結果な「ノ」出たら、どうしよう？}What will I do, if the results turn out to be a "no"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{何もかも終わりだわ。}Everything will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:23:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんなに張り切ってXXX柏木さんたちグループのXXXも動力も…希望も…皆の夢…}Kashiwagi-san's group's energy… their spirit… their hopes… our dream…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしを寝台して京間でついてきてくれた皆に…なんと言ったら謝ればいいの？}After they made me their coach and followed me this far, how will I apologize to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{あゆはらさん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{お待たせしました。}Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{いかがでしょう？}How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.91,0:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生…}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:55.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{レントゲン写真にじっと見る医者の表情は固い。}The doctor's gaze over radiograph is long and inscrutable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:24:00.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{だが、バレーボールに打ち込んだ若い生命力は、見事に病気を直していたのだ。}However, the youthful devotion to the volleyball seems to have helped in curing the illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:07.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{いよいよ試合の日。こずえの率いる不良チームたいバレー部の解決は嫌な上にも任侠呼んだ。}Finally, the day of the match. The useless group led by Kozue settles things out with the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:12.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{不良チームは、一ヶ月激しいトレーニングの成果をXXXだが、}The extreme training spanning one month seems to have fruited, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:15.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{大勢の慣習の前にしてしっかり固くなり…}…the useless group tenses up in front of a crowd of spectators.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.12,0:24:18.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{バレー部のなすがままに、とくてんはどんどんひらいていく。}Unfazed, the volleyball club has no intention of going easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.80,0:24:24.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワン：「新キャプテン誕生」お楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
